{"tid":574464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無紅斑狼瘡嘅巴絲打 可以入黎吹下水","createTime":"2018-02-27T11:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T14:59:04.000Z","uid":169271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fab44fc7b5a176dd8b8efa02d355051ceb26e709","tid":574464,"uid":169271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"有左而個病半年左右<br />\n最近開始越黎越嚴重<br />\n覺得自從有左而個病之後<br />\n雖然外表 同正常人無咩分別<br />\n但自己知道身體內在好多野都已經唔同左<br />\n一病就好難好返<br />\n又成日病<br />\n成日關節痛 等等等<br />\n基本上無一日係覺得舒服<br />\n好影響日常生活 好驚關節痛會影響第時做野<br />\n唔知食幾耐藥先會真正開始見效<br />\n越黎越多病徵陸續出現<br />\n唔知仲會有咩可怕嘅病徵黎緊出現<br />\n越諗越灰<br />\n好想同樣有而個病嘅你 可以留低tg<br />\n大家間唔中互相鼓勵下"},{"pid":"66150eaee8840dd7191df0cb77da4d9e6c88b007","tid":574464,"uid":126657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"我記得小喬都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝願快啲有藥醫 爸打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71093ab761bd9f601e6b3368b42e96eb3bb1491d","tid":574464,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67e9e94f2c3f69a3b34d3e3cf82935ce0c7b49a","tid":574464,"uid":11462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71093ab761bd9f601e6b3368b42e96eb3bb1491d","tid":574464,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T19:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d8ace94bf4e12b1888fb1f9ffc51eb6faa1dc